- Preferences: well‑curated remastered hits collections; tape‑like analog warmth and dynamics (low compression); forward, close‑mic lead vocals and clear midrange; prominent/tasteful Hammond organ; tasteful/gritty but restrained guitar; punchy groove‑driven drums and bass; tight, performance‑led 3–4 minute, hook‑first tracks built for replay appeal; careful sequencing and collector‑grade mastering/packaging.
